":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:06.927","remediation":"升级 Analog 至 4.0 以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本修复。如无法升级，可在 Web 服务器配置中限制对 Analog forms 接口的访问，或禁用 forms 功能，仅允许授信 IP 访问。同时避免将 Analog 的 CGI 接口放置在公网可访问目录下。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.statslab.cam.ac.uk/~sret1/analog/security.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1410","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1287.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1287","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1287.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1287.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-f974-p775-h8x3/GHSA-f974-p775-h8x3.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87844/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1287.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8358776d7db47304e3a87c0f78eff81411ac0e47/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1031.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1030","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1030.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1279","title":"IBM AS/400 与 Microsoft SNA Server 共享文件夹信息泄露漏洞","description":"AS/400 共享文件夹功能与 Microsoft SNA Server 3.0 及更早版本交互时存在权限控制缺陷。当多个用户共享相同的本地 APPC LU（逻辑单元）时，SNA Server 未能正确隔离用户之间的文件夹访问权限，导致用户可越权查看其他用户的共享文件夹内容，造成敏感信息泄露。攻击者只需在共享同一 APPC LU 的环境中拥有合法用户身份即可利用，无需额外认证或复杂操作。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1279"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:05.937","remediation":"升级至 Microsoft SNA Server 4.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复共享 Local APPC LU 导致的文件夹泄露问题。如无法升级，可为每个用户配置独立的 Local APPC LU 别名，避免不同用户共享同一 LU，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q138/0/01.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1548","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1279.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1279","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1279.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1279.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3qcq-w2m6-vwwx/GHSA-3qcq-w2m6-vwwx.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87845/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1279.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001013.txt","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/windows.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1030.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1026","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1026.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1259","title":"Microsoft Office 98 Macintosh Edition 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft Office 98 Macintosh 版在创建文件时未对分配的磁盘空间进行初始化清理，导致先前删除文件中的残留数据被写入新创建的 Office 文件中，造成敏感信息泄露。攻击者通过获取目标用户的 Office 文档，即可从中提取可能包含密码、私人通信等内容的残余数据。该漏洞影响 Office 98 Macintosh Edition，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，需本地文件访问权限方可利用。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1259"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:03.430","remediation":"建议升级至 Microsoft Office 2001 for Mac 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。作为临时缓解措施，在保存 Office 文件前使用磁盘擦除工具对文件存储区域进行清零处理，或使用文件加密软件保护敏感数据以防止信息泄露。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q189/5/29.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1780","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1259.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1259","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1259.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1259.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4fg5-9xqq-h6cq/GHSA-4fg5-9xqq-h6cq.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87853/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1259.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_infor.txt","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/windows.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1026.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1012","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1012.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1223","title":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 ASP 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 的 ASP 功能处理 URL 时存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送包含大量 \"/\" 字符的恶意 URL 请求至 ASP 页面，触发 IIS 服务进程消耗过多系统资源而导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 IIS 3.0 版本，攻击复杂度低，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1223"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:58.883","remediation":"升级至 Microsoft IIS 4.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，可通过 URLScan 工具限制请求路径长度，或配置 IIS 过滤器拦截包含超长路径的 ASP 请求以缓解 DoS 风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q187/5/03.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3892","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-1223.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1223.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1223","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1223.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1223.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cj4j-jmwc-f6jm/GHSA-cj4j-jmwc-f6jm.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87550/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1223.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1012.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1012.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1012.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1011","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1011.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1222","title":"微软 Windows NT 4.0 Netbt.sys 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 系统的 Netbt.sys 驱动（负责 NetBIOS over TCP/IP 名称解析）存在拒绝服务漏洞。当系统作为客户端向远程 DNS 服务器发起主机名查询时，若攻击者能够控制或伪造该 DNS 服务器（例如通过中间人攻击或劫持 DNS 响应），使其返回一个 IP 地址为 0.0.0.0 的异常解析结果，Netbt.sys 在处理该非法地址时会触发缺陷，导致系统崩溃并停止响应。该漏洞仅影响 Windows NT 4.0 操作系统，攻击条件为攻击者能够向目标主机返回恶意构造的 DNS 解析响应，利用方式是通过操纵 DNS 服务器返回 0.0.0.0 地址以引发远程拒绝服务。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1222"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:58.753","remediation":"建议立即升级至 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 或更高版本（如 Windows 2000/XP/Server 2003），并应用微软安全公告 MS99-037 发布的补丁（Q269874）。若无法立即升级，请在防火墙层面限制仅允许受信任的 DNS 服务器（如企业内部 DNS），禁止外部 DNS 解析请求，并在主机防火墙层面禁止 NetBIOS over TCP/IP（NetBT）协议端口（UDP/TCP 137、138、139、445）对外暴露，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["h